                  </hi>. I saw the prisoner's hand in the prosecutor's window—he then rushed out of the door, knocked the child down, and ran away—I ran, and brought him back—he was very resistible indeed.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I went in there for a halfpenny-worth of nails—this man then said I had taken something, but I had not—I went out, and went up Moor-lane, and was then brought back.</p>
